of your model universe.

00:07:24.250 --> 00:07:27.480
So what you would say is that
the total density of things

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:31.650
in your universe is a sum
over whatever mixture of stuff

00:07:31.650 --> 00:07:33.098
is in your universe.

00:07:37.490 --> 00:07:40.340
You will find it helpful to
specify an equation of state

00:07:40.340 --> 00:07:41.750
for each species.

00:07:41.750 --> 00:07:43.823
Cosmologists typically
choose equation of state

00:07:43.823 --> 00:07:44.990
that has the following form.

00:08:00.890 --> 00:08:01.390
OK.

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:03.070
So you require your species--

00:08:03.070 --> 00:08:07.060
