Now what we really want to do--

00:09:52.180 --> 00:09:52.680
OK.

00:09:52.680 --> 00:09:55.050
We are physicists.

00:09:55.050 --> 00:09:57.690
And our goal in
doing these models

00:09:57.690 --> 00:10:02.310
